            <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i>
            <strong>‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡πÄ‡∏ï‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏ô:</strong> 
            <ul class="mb-0 mt-2">
              <li>‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå CSV ‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏°‡∏µ header row (‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏Ñ‡∏≠‡∏•‡∏±‡∏°‡∏ô‡πå)</li>
